    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Average time to complete the game: 40 minutes</u></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056960/extras/fbc1c1c69d6721e141b5801e1e0b4111.poster.avif?t=1756925782\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056960/extras/fbc1c1c69d6721e141b5801e1e0b4111.webm?t=1756925782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056960/extras/fbc1c1c69d6721e141b5801e1e0b4111.mp4?t=1756925782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since the city was abandoned, no one has dared to return. Now, you want to search for information that helps you understand what happened before and during the virus outbreak. Find a way to explore the city and discover the hotel where it all began. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INVESTIGATE THE MYSTERY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the dark secrets behind the tragic events at the City of Nightmares. Piece together information, gather evidence, and solve intricate puzzles to find out what happened to the guests and how all of them died. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056960/extras/e8e5596f36858ac2961e64b302330651.poster.avif?t=1756925782\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056960/extras/e8e5596f36858ac2961e64b302330651.webm?t=1756925782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056960/extras/e8e5596f36858ac2961e64b302330651.mp4?t=1756925782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENCOUNTER GHOSTLY PRESENCES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Along your journey, you'll encounter restless spirits and supernatural entities </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-Person Exploration</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive Environments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evidence Gathering and Puzzle Solving</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haunted Hotel Setting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghostly Encounters and Paranormal Events</p>",
